data.description: Exceptional Investment Opportunity! Discover this huge, beautiful 3-family home in the heart of Newark. Each of the 3-bedroom apartments, spanning 1500 sq feet, features gleaming hardwood floors, exceptionally large bedrooms, spacious living rooms with a balcony, an open dining room, a laundry room, and a master suite with ample closet space, an en-suite bathroom, and a private balcony. The home boasts a built-in, oversized double garage with storage closets for tenants. It sits on a large fenced-in lot that can accommodate parking for up to 6 cars. The property will be sold with two large 3-bedroom units vacant and a tenant currently occupying the 2-bedroom apartment on the ground floor. Offering immense value, this home is not expected to last long on the market. Ideally located close to parks, restaurants, shopping, public transportation, major highways, and NYC.
